code: @Test public void testSendMatchingMessage() throws Exception {     String expectedBody = "<matched/>".     resultEndpoint.expectedBodiesReceived(expectedBody).     template.sendBodyAndHeader(expectedBody, "foo", "bar").     resultEndpoint.assertIsSatisfied(). }

@Test public void testSendNotMatchingMessage() throws Exception {     resultEndpoint.expectedMessageCount(0).     template.sendBodyAndHeader("<notMatched/>", "foo", "notMatchedHeaderValue").     resultEndpoint.assertIsSatisfied(). }
